t = int(input())
    for i in range(t):
        s = input()
        n = len(s)
        dp = [0]*(n+1)
        dp[0] = 1
        dp[1] = 1
        for i in range(2,n+1):
            if s[i-1] > '0':
                dp[i] = dp[i-1]
            if s[i-2] == '1' or (s[i-2] == '2' and s[i-1] < '7'):
                dp[i] += dp[i-2]
        print(dp[n]%1000000007)
